add to a vibrant and crunchy celery slaw with an extra burst of flavour from ponzu sauce - a Japanese pantry staple with a
kick of citrus. Sprinkle over some crushed peanuts and go for your life.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving*

